msgctxt "68_Short-Haired High School Girl"
msgid "They went up the street. You know, toward the theater?"
msgstr "Subieron por la calle. Creo que al teatro."

msgctxt "80_Hair Bun High School Girl"
msgid "They really stood out. I bet a lot of other people saw\r\n"
"them, too."
msgstr "Llamaban bastante la atención. Apuesto a que muchas otras personas los vieron también."

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "Excuse me, do you have a moment?"
msgstr "Disculpen, ¿puedo preguntarles algo?"

msgctxt "104_Hair Bun High School Girl"
msgid "Hm? What's up?"
msgstr "¿Eh? Claro."

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "Have you seen a group of yakuza around here? They probably\r\n"
"had someone who looked all beat up with them..."
msgstr "¿Han visto un grupo de yakuzas por aquí? Puede que llevaran a alguien golpeado con ellos..."

msgctxt "128_Short-Haired High School Girl"
msgid "Oh yeah, I saw them! They were dragging some guy through\r\n"
"town."
msgstr "¡Ah, sí, los vi! Estaban arrastrando a un tipo\r\n"
"por la ciudad."

msgctxt "140_Hair Bun High School Girl"
msgid "They were really scary! They kept telling him to walk\r\n"
"faster!"
msgstr "¡Daban miedo! ¡No paraban de decirle que caminara rápido!"

msgctxt "152_Akiyama"
msgid "See where they went?"
msgstr "¿Vieron a dónde fueron?"

msgctxt "164_Short-Haired High School Girl"
msgid "They went up the street. You know, toward the theater?"
msgstr "Subieron por la calle. Creo que al teatro."

msgctxt "176_Hair Bun High School Girl"
msgid "They really stood out. I bet a lot of other people saw\r\n"
"them, too."
msgstr "Llamaban bastante la atención. Apuesto a que muchas otras personas los vieron también."

msgctxt "188_Akiyama"
msgid "That right? Okay, thanks."
msgstr "¿En serio? Bien, gracias."

